data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"Implemented `index.html` with the approved local assets, roofing-specific copy, phone/form quote path, local SEO metadata, and RoofingContractor JSON-LD. Structural checks passed.\n\n<artifact identifier=\"ridgeline-roof-co-home\" type=\"text/html\" title=\"RidgeLine Roof Co. Home Page\">\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>RidgeLine Roof Co. | Roofing Contractor Brisbane & Gold Coast</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"RidgeLine Roof Co. provides roof repairs, restoration, metal roofing, gutter repairs, and roof inspections across Brisbane and the Gold Coast.\" />\n  <meta name=\"review-provenance\" content=\"ai-reference-placeholder; replace with real Google or customer reviews before live\" />\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n  {\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"RoofingContractor\",\n    \"name\": \"RidgeLine Roof Co.\",\n    \"telephone\": \"0400 000 000\",\n    \"url\": \"\",\n    \"address\": {\n      \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n      \"addressLocality\": \"Brisbane\",\n      \"addressRegion\": \"QLD\",\n      \"addressCountry\": \"AU\"\n    },\n    \"areaServed\": [\"Brisbane\", \"Gold Coast\"],\n    \"priceRange\": \"\",\n    \"sameAs\": [],\n    \"hasMap\": \"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Brisbane+roofing+contractor\",\n    \"description\": \"Local roofing contractor for roof repairs, roof restoration, metal roofing, gutter repairs, and roof inspections.\"\n  }\n  </script>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg: oklch(98% 0.004 92);\n      --surface: oklch(100% 0 0);\n      --fg: oklch(14% 0.01 70);\n      --muted: oklch(43% 0.012 70);\n      --border: oklch(86% 0.012 85);\n      --accent: oklch(64% 0.18 43);\n\n      --accent-soft: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 14%, transparent);\n      --fg-soft: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 6%, transparent);\n      --ink-panel: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 94%, var(--accent));\n\n      --font-display: Impact, Haettenschweiler, 'Arial Narrow Bold', 'Franklin Gothic Heavy', sans-serif;\n      --font-body: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;\n      --font-mono: ui-monospace, 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', Menlo, monospace;\n\n      --fs-h1: clamp(58px, 9vw, 132px);\n      --fs-h2: clamp(34px, 5vw, 74px);\n      --fs-h3: 24px;\n      --fs-lead: 20px;\n      --fs-body: 16px;\n      --fs-meta: 13px;\n\n      --gap-md: 20px;\n      --gap-lg: 32px;\n      --gap-xl: 56px;\n      --gap-2xl: 96px;\n      --container: 1180px;\n      --gutter: 28px;\n      --radius: 4px;\n    }\n\n    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; scroll-behavior: smooth; }\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--fg);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      font-size: var(--fs-body);\n      line-height: 1.55;\n      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\n      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n    }\n    img { display: block; max-width: 100%; }\n    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }\n    button, input, textarea, select { font: inherit; }\n    p { text-wrap: pretty; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { text-wrap: balance; }\n\n    .container { max-width: var(--container); margin-inline: auto; padding-inline: var(--gutter); }\n    .section { padding-block: clamp(58px, 8vw, var(--gap-2xl)); }\n    .section + .section { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .row-between { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n\n    h1, h2, h3 {\n      font-family: var(--font-display);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0;\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n    h1 { font-size: var(--fs-h1); line-height: 0.9; }\n    h2 { font-size: var(--fs-h2); line-height: 0.92; }\n    h3 { font-size: var(--fs-h3); line-height: 1; }\n    .lead { font-size: var(--fs-lead); line-height: 1.5; color: var(--muted); max-width: 58ch; margin: 0; }\n    .eyebrow {\n      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n      font-size: 12px;\n      letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin: 0 0 var(--gap-md);\n    }\n    .meta, .num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-meta); color: var(--muted); }\n    .num { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\n\n    .topnav {\n      position: sticky;\n      top: 0;\n      z-index: 20;\n      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--bg) 92%, transparent);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n    .topnav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-block: 13px; }\n    .logo { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 24px; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 1; }\n    .logo-mark { width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--fg); color: var(--surface); display: grid; place-items: center; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; }\n    .topnav nav { display: flex; gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .topnav nav a { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); }\n    .topnav nav a:hover { color: var(--fg); }\n    .mobile-call { display: none; }\n\n    .btn {\n      display: inline-flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      gap: 8px;\n      min-height: 44px;\n      padding: 12px 22px;\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      border: 1px solid transparent;\n      font-size: 15px;\n      font-weight: 800;\n      letter-spacing: 0.02em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      transition: transform 0.05s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;\n    }\n    .btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }\n    .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: var(--fg); border-color: var(--accent); }\n    .btn-primary:hover { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 86%, var(--surface)); }\n    .btn-secondary { background: var(--fg); color: var(--surface); border-color: var(--fg); }\n    .btn-secondary:hover { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 88%, var(--accent)); }\n    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); border-color: var(--border); }\n    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--fg); }\n    .btn-arrow::after { content: '->'; font-family: var(--font-mono); transition: transform 0.15s ease; }\n    .btn-arrow:hover::after { transform: translateX(2px); }\n\n    .hero-poster {\n      min-height: calc(100svh - 72px);\n      display: grid;\n      align-items: end;\n      padding-block: clamp(40px, 6vw, 82px);\n      position: relative;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .hero-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.06fr) minmax(310px, 0.94fr);\n      gap: clamp(28px, 5vw, 64px);\n      align-items: end;\n    }\n    .hero-copy { position: relative; z-index: 2; }\n    .hero-copy h1 { max-width: 9ch; }\n    .hero-copy .lead { margin-top: 24px; max-width: 40ch; color: var(--fg); }\n    .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 28px; }\n    .service-strip { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 30px; max-width: 640px; }\n    .tag {\n      display: inline-flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      padding: 5px 10px;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 70%, transparent);\n      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n      font-size: 12px;\n    }\n    .hero-photo-wrap { position: relative; isolation: isolate; }\n    .hero-photo-wrap::before {\n      content: '';\n      position: absolute;\n      inset: 10% -6% -5% 18%;\n      background: var(--accent);\n      z-index: -1;\n    }\n    .hero-photo {\n      width: 100%;\n      aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;\n      object-fit: cover;\n      border: 1px solid var(--fg);\n      filter: saturate(0.94) contrast(1.04);\n    }\n    .hero-note {\n      position: absolute;\n      left: -26px;\n      bottom: 34px;\n      width: min(310px, 70%);\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--fg);\n      padding: 16px;\n      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n    }\n\n    .marquee-band {\n      border-block: 1px solid var(--fg);\n      background: var(--surface);\n      overflow: hidden;\n      padding-block: 14px;\n    }\n    .marquee-band p {\n      margin: 0;\n      white-space: nowrap;\n      font-family: var(--font-display);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      font-size: clamp(30px, 5vw, 72px);\n      line-height: 0.9;\n      color: var(--fg);\n    }\n\n    .service-row {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 86px 1fr minmax(220px, 0.8fr);\n      gap: var(--gap-lg);\n      padding: 26px 0;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n      align-items: start;\n    }\n    .service-row:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .service-row .num { color: var(--accent); }\n    .service-row p { margin: 6px 0 0; color: var(--muted); max-width: 42ch; }\n    .service-image { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16 / 10; object-fit: cover; border: 1px solid var(--border); }\n\n    .dark-panel { background: var(--ink-panel); color: var(--surface); border-top: 0; }\n    .dark-panel .eyebrow { color: var(--accent); }\n    .dark-panel .lead, .dark-panel .meta { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 68%, transparent); }\n    .story-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: center; }\n    .story-photo-stack { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.78fr; gap: 14px; align-items: end; }\n    .story-photo-stack img { width: 100%; object-fit: cover; border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 32%, transparent); filter: saturate(0.9) contrast(1.08); }\n    .story-photo-stack img:first-child { aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }\n    .story-photo-stack img:last-child { aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; margin-bottom: 56px; }\n    .proof-list { display: grid; gap: 18px; margin-top: 30px; }\n    .proof-item { border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 22%, transparent); padding-top: 18px; }\n    .proof-item strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 22px; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n\n    .work-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; gap: var(--gap-lg); align-items: stretch; }\n    .work-grid img { width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 320px; object-fit: cover; border: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .work-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface); padding: clamp(24px, 4vw, 42px); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--gap-xl); }\n    .work-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: grid; gap: 12px; }\n    .work-card li { display: flex; gap: 10px; color: var(--muted); }\n    .work-card li::before { content: '/'; color: var(--fg); font-family: var(--font-mono); }\n\n    .process-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(260px, 0.8fr) 1.2fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    .step { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr; gap: var(--gap-md); padding: 22px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .step h3 { margin-bottom: 6px; }\n    .step p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); }\n    .quote-box { position: sticky; top: 96px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--fg); padding: 24px; }\n    .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }\n    .field label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }\n    .input, .textarea, .select {\n      width: 100%;\n      padding: 12px 14px;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      background: var(--surface);\n      color: var(--fg);\n      font: inherit;\n      font-size: 15px;\n    }\n    .input:focus, .textarea:focus, .select:focus { outline: 2px solid var(--accent-soft); border-color: var(--accent); }\n    .textarea { min-height: 116px; resize: vertical; line-height: 1.55; }\n    .form-grid { display: grid; gap: 14px; margin-top: 22px; }\n\n    .faq-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 0.78fr 1.22fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    .faq-item { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 20px 0; }\n    .faq-item p { margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--muted); }\n    .contact-card { background: var(--fg); color: var(--surface); padding: clamp(26px, 4vw, 44px); min-height: 100%; }\n    .contact-card .lead, .contact-card .meta { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 70%, transparent); }\n    .contact-card a:hover { color: var(--accent); }\n\n    .pagefoot { padding-block: var(--gap-xl); color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .pagefoot .row-between { flex-wrap: wrap; }\n\n    @media (max-width: 980px) {\n      .grid-2, .hero-grid, .story-grid, .work-grid, .process-grid, .faq-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .topnav nav { display: none; }\n      .topnav .btn-primary { display: none; }\n      .mobile-call { display: inline-flex; }\n      .hero-poster { min-height: auto; align-items: start; }\n      .hero-copy h1 { max-width: 7.6ch; }\n      .hero-note { left: 14px; bottom: 14px; }\n      .service-row { grid-template-columns: 52px 1fr; }\n      .service-row .service-image { grid-column: 1 / -1; }\n      .quote-box { position: static; }\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 640px) {\n      :root { --gutter: 18px; --fs-h1: clamp(52px, 18vw, 82px); }\n      .row-between { align-items: flex-start; }\n      .hero-cta .btn { width: 100%; }\n      .hero-photo { aspect-ratio: 4 / 4.8; }\n      .story-photo-stack { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .story-photo-stack img:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }\n      .step { grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header class=\"topnav\" data-od-id=\"topnav\">\n    <div class=\"container topnav-inner\">\n      <a class=\"logo\" href=\"#top\" aria-label=\"RidgeLine Roof Co. home\">\n        <span class=\"logo-mark\">RL</span>\n        RidgeLine Roof Co.\n      </a>\n      <nav aria-label=\"Primary navigation\">\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#work\">Roof work</a>\n        <a href=\"#quote\">Quote process</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n      </nav>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"tel:0400000000\">Call 0400 000 000</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary mobile-call\" href=\"tel:0400000000\">Call</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main id=\"content\">\n    <section class=\"section hero-poster\" data-od-id=\"hero\" id=\"top\">\n      <div class=\"container hero-grid\">\n        <div class=\"hero-copy\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Roof repairs · Restoration · Metal roofing</p>\n          <h1>Roofing for Brisbane and Gold Coast properties</h1>\n          <p class=\"lead\">RidgeLine Roof Co. handles repairs, restorations, inspections, gutter work, and metal roofing with a clear quote path from first call to site visit.</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-cta\">\n            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#quote\">Request inspection</a>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-arrow\" href=\"tel:0400000000\">Call 0400 000 000</a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"service-strip\" aria-label=\"Core roofing services\">\n            <span class=\"tag\">Roof repairs</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Roof restoration</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Metal roofing</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Gutter repairs</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Roof inspections</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-photo-wrap\">\n          <img class=\"hero-photo\" src=\"assets/hero-family2-hero-worker-standing-metal-roof-wide.png\" alt=\"Roofing contractor standing on a metal roof during a roof inspection\" />\n          <div class=\"hero-note\">Serving Brisbane and the Gold Coast. Use the form below to describe the roof issue, property type, and preferred inspection window.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"marquee-band\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n      <p>Roof inspections / repairs / restorations / metal roofing / gutter repairs /</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"services\" id=\"services\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row-between\" style=\"margin-bottom: 42px;\">\n          <div style=\"max-width: 760px;\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Services</p>\n            <h2>Practical roof work without brochure clutter</h2>\n          </div>\n          <a class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-arrow\" href=\"#quote\">Start a quote</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <article class=\"service-row\">\n          <span class=\"num\">01</span>\n          <div>\n            <h3>Roof repairs</h3>\n            <p>Targeted repair work for leaks, storm damage, flashing issues, loose sheets, cracked tiles, and localised wear.</p>\n          </div>\n          <img class=\"service-image\" src=\"assets/service-family2-service-roofer-metal-roof-diagonal.png\" alt=\"Roofer working across a diagonal metal roof surface\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"service-row\">\n          <span class=\"num\">02</span>\n          <div>\n            <h3>Roof restoration</h3>\n            <p>Inspection-led restoration planning for tired roofs, surface wear, water ingress risks, and homes preparing for sale or renovation.</p>\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"meta\">Residential and light commercial</span>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"service-row\">\n          <span class=\"num\">03</span>\n          <div>\n            <h3>Metal roofing</h3>\n            <p>Metal roof assessment, repair, and replacement pathways for properties that need a cleaner, stronger roof finish.</p>\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"meta\">Material and access reviewed on site</span>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"service-row\">\n          <span class=\"num\">04</span>\n          <div>\n            <h3>Gutter repairs</h3>\n            <p>Gutter leaks, fall problems, rusted sections, storm overflow, and roofline drainage issues checked alongside the roof.</p>\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"meta\">Roofline drainage focus</span>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"service-row\">\n          <span class=\"num\">05</span>\n          <div>\n            <h3>Roof inspections</h3>\n            <p>A site visit to identify visible issues, photo-document the concern areas, and give you a clear next step.</p>\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"meta\">Quote pathway starts here</span>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section dark-panel\" data-od-id=\"proof\">\n      <div class=\"container story-grid\">\n        <div class=\"story-photo-stack\">\n          <img src=\"assets/story-family2-story-two-roofers-metal-roof-portrait.png\" alt=\"Two roofers inspecting a roof surface together\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n          <img src=\"assets/projectTile-family2-service-orange-accent-roof-work.png\" alt=\"Close view of roof work with an orange accent tool on site\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">How the work feels</p>\n          <h2>Commercial confidence, local quote process</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 22px;\">A roof issue is usually urgent, but the decision should not feel rushed. RidgeLine keeps the path simple: inspect the roof, explain the finding, then quote the right level of work.</p>\n          <div class=\"proof-list\">\n            <div class=\"proof-item\">\n              <strong>Site-first assessment</strong>\n              <span class=\"meta\">Roof access, material type, drainage, visible wear, and safety conditions are checked before scope is discussed.</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"proof-item\">\n              <strong>Clear repair language</strong>\n              <span class=\"meta\">Plain explanations of leak points, corrosion, cracked surfaces, flashing, gutters, and restoration options.</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"proof-item\">\n              <strong>Project-ready structure</strong>\n              <span class=\"meta\">Inspection notes can separate immediate repairs from restoration items, so the quote is easier to understand and compare.</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"featured-work\" id=\"work\">\n      <div class=\"container work-grid\">\n        <img src=\"assets/projectDetail-family2-project-commercial-metal-roof-detail.png\" alt=\"Detailed commercial metal roofing surface with clean roof lines\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n        <div class=\"work-card\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Roof work</p>\n            <h2>Made concrete before anyone climbs a ladder</h2>\n          </div>\n          <ul>\n            <li>Tell us the property suburb, roof type if known, and what you can see from the ground.</li>\n            <li>Upload or describe visible leak marks, rust, cracked tiles, loose sheets, or gutter overflow.</li>\n            <li>Ask for repair, restoration, metal roofing, gutter repair, or inspection advice in one place.</li>\n            <li>For urgent leaks, calling is the fastest route.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"quote-process\" id=\"quote\">\n      <div class=\"container process-grid\">\n        <aside class=\"quote-box\" aria-label=\"Quote enquiry form\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Request a quote</p>\n          <h2 style=\"font-size: clamp(34px, 4vw, 58px);\">Tell us what the roof is doing</h2>\n          <form class=\"form-grid\" action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n            <div class=\"field\">\n              <label for=\"name\">Name</label>\n              <input class=\"input\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" autocomplete=\"name\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field\">\n              <label for=\"phone\">Phone</label>\n              <input class=\"input\" id=\"phone\" name=\"phone\" inputmode=\"tel\" autocomplete=\"tel\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field\">\n              <label for=\"suburb\">Suburb</label>\n              <input class=\"input\" id=\"suburb\" name=\"suburb\" autocomplete=\"address-level2\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field\">\n              <label for=\"service\">What do you need?</label>\n              <select class=\"select\" id=\"service\" name=\"service\">\n                <option>Roof inspection</option>\n                <option>Roof repair</option>\n                <option>Roof restoration</option>\n                <option>Metal roofing</option>\n                <option>Gutter repair</option>\n              </select>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field\">\n              <label for=\"message\">Roof notes</label>\n              <textarea class=\"textarea\" id=\"message\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Leak location, visible damage, roof material, timing, or access notes\"></textarea>\n            </div>\n            <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">Send enquiry</button>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-arrow\" href=\"tel:0400000000\">Or call 0400 000 000</a>\n          </form>\n        </aside>\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Quote process</p>\n          <h2>From roof concern to next step</h2>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 34px;\">\n            <div class=\"step\">\n              <span class=\"num\">01</span>\n              <div>\n                <h3>Send the roof concern</h3>\n                <p>Use the form or call with the suburb, property type, and what has changed: leak, storm damage, visible rust, cracked tile, or gutter overflow.</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"step\">\n              <span class=\"num\">02</span>\n              <div>\n                <h3>Book an inspection window</h3>\n                <p>A practical site visit is arranged so access, safety, roof material, and likely repair scope can be checked properly.</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"step\">\n              <span class=\"num\">03</span>\n              <div>\n                <h3>Receive a clear scope</h3>\n                <p>You get a plain-language explanation of the issue and the proposed repair, restoration, or roofing pathway.</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"faq-contact-footer\" id=\"contact\">\n      <div class=\"container faq-grid\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Questions</p>\n          <h2>Before you book</h2>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"faq-item\">\n            <h3>Do you inspect roofs across both Brisbane and the Gold Coast?</h3>\n            <p>Yes. RidgeLine Roof Co. presents this service area as Brisbane and the Gold Coast. Confirm suburb availability when you call or send the enquiry.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-item\">\n            <h3>Can you quote without seeing the roof?</h3>\n            <p>Photos and notes help triage the issue, but roof access, material condition, and safety requirements usually need a site inspection before quoting accurately.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-item\">\n            <h3>What should I include in the enquiry?</h3>\n            <p>Include the suburb, roof type if known, the visible issue, when it started, and whether there are active leaks or storm-related concerns.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-item\">\n            <h3>Do you handle gutters as well as roofing?</h3>\n            <p>Yes. Gutter repairs are part of the listed services, especially where overflow or drainage is affecting the roofline.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"container\" style=\"margin-top: 58px;\">\n        <div class=\"contact-card\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div>\n              <p class=\"eyebrow\">Contact</p>\n              <h2>Ready for a roof inspection?</h2>\n              <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 18px;\">Call now or send the form above with the roof issue and suburb. For active leaks, phone is the fastest path.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stack\">\n              <p><strong>Phone</strong><br><a href=\"tel:0400000000\">0400 000 000</a></p>\n              <p><strong>Service area</strong><br>Brisbane and Gold Coast</p>\n              <p><strong>Hours</strong><br>Contact for current inspection availability</p>\n              <p><strong>Directions</strong><br><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Brisbane+roofing+contractor\">Open Brisbane roofing contractor map search</a></p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"pagefoot\" data-od-id=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"container row-between\">\n      <span>© 2026 RidgeLine Roof Co. · Local roofing contractor</span>\n      <span class=\"meta\">Roof repairs · Roof restoration · Metal roofing · Gutter repairs · Roof inspections</span>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n</artifact>"}

